post_text: Enrollment is scheduled for July 29th, 30th, 31st, and August 3rd. In order to meet the needs of all students, Turner will be offering two different learning plans for the upcoming school year. Students who want to attend class in person will have the option of the traditional learning plan and those students who prefer to stay home will have the option of a virtual online learning plan. Each student will choose their learning plan at enrollment. If you have any questions please contact Brenda Foster at 580-276-1307 ext.200 , Miranda Shelton at 580-276-1307 ext. 300 or Heather Hill Counselor at 580-276-1307 ext. 503
